1935;;The Lad;;British;;Henry Edwards;;Gordon Harker, Betty Stockfeld;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Lad;;Bill Shane is The Lad, an opportunistic petty criminal mistaken for a private detective. When Shane arrives at a remote country estate, he's offered lots of money not to delve into the private affairs of the Fandon family. Shane is all for taking the money and duping the family, but on being reunited with ex-girlfriend Pauline, now the Fandon's maid, he decides to turn over a new leaf.